      "description": "<p>Corpo a corpo, Invocação</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\">Com alguns movimentos manuais cria gafanhotos a partir dos próprios braços, eles atacam tudo no caminho determinado.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Esforço:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 3.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo de preparo:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 1 ação.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> trajeto de 15m.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> [8+ESP</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">].</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"> Indireto. Dano diminui em 2 por alvo atingido até mínimo de 1.</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Pré-requisitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> Sabakismo N1.</span></p>",
